snippet.title: Longplay of Nicktoons Racing
snippet.description:
Longplay of Nicktoons Racing, played as the PAL version on the Game Boy Advance. This game's version was released on June 14th, 2002. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Opening
00:16 - Intro
01:26 - Nearburg Rally as CatDog
03:11 - Mrs. Puff's Driving School as SpongeBob SquarePants
04:55 - Reptar Raceway as Tommy Pickles
07:10 - Congo Bongo Bang Up as Darwin
09:41 - Pickles Parkway as Angelica Pickles
11:31 - Safari Speedway as Eliza Thornberry
13:11 - Gritty City Circuit as Helga
15:20 - Beaver Fever as The Angry Beavers
17:38 - Ahh...Real Racing as Ickis
19:29 - Jazz Mattazz as Arnold
21:28 - Race Madness as Stimpy
23:17 - Bikini Bottom Blowout as Patrick Star
25:22 - Credits

By: SpectreBull
